#: src/languages/python.md:54
msgid ""
"`node_id` (str, optional) -- Explicit node ID for dynamic nodes. When "
"omitted, the node reads its identity from environment variables set by the "
"adora daemon."
msgstr ""
"`node_id`（str，可选）—— 动态节点的显式节点 ID。省略时，节点从 adora 守护进程"
"设置的环境变量中读取身份。"

#: src/languages/python.md:56
msgid "**Raises:** `RuntimeError` if the node cannot connect to the dataflow."
msgstr "**异常：** 如果节点无法连接到数据流，则抛出 `RuntimeError`。"

#: src/languages/python.md:60
msgid "`next(timeout=None)`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/python.md:62
msgid ""
"Retrieve the next event from the event stream. Blocks until an event is "
"available or the timeout expires."
msgstr "从事件流中获取下一个事件。阻塞直到有事件可用或超时过期。"

#: src/languages/python.md:65
msgid "# block indefinitely\n"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/python.md:66
msgid "# block up to 2 seconds\n"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/python.md:70
msgid "`timeout` (float, optional) -- Maximum wait time in seconds."
msgstr "`timeout`（float，可选）—— 最大等待时间（秒）。"

#: src/languages/python.md:72
msgid ""
"**Returns:** `dict` -- An [event dictionary](#event-dictionary), or `None` "
"if all senders have been dropped or the timeout expired."
msgstr ""
"**返回：** `dict` —— 一个[事件字典](#event-dictionary)，如果所有发送者已被释"
"放或超时过期则为 `None`。"

#: src/languages/python.md:76
msgid "`drain()`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/python.md:78
msgid "Retrieve all buffered events without blocking."
msgstr "非阻塞地获取所有缓冲事件。"

#: src/languages/python.md:86
msgid ""
"**Returns:** `list[dict]` -- A list of [event dictionaries](#event-"
"dictionary). Returns an empty list if no events are buffered."
msgstr ""
"**返回：** `list[dict]` —— [事件字典](#event-dictionary)列表。如果没有缓冲事"
"件则返回空列表。"

#: src/languages/python.md:90
msgid "`try_recv()`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/python.md:92
msgid ""
"Non-blocking receive. Returns the next buffered event if one is available."
msgstr "非阻塞接收。如果有可用的缓冲事件则返回。"

#: src/languages/python.md:100
msgid ""
"**Returns:** `dict | None` -- An [event dictionary](#event-dictionary), or "
"`None` if no event is buffered."
msgstr ""
"**返回：** `dict | None` —— 一个[事件字典](#event-dictionary)，如果没有缓冲事"
"件则为 `None`。"

#: src/languages/python.md:104
msgid "`recv_async(timeout=None)`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/python.md:106
msgid "Asynchronous receive. For use with `asyncio`."
msgstr "异步接收。配合 `asyncio` 使用。"

#: src/languages/python.md:114
msgid ""
"`timeout` (float, optional) -- Maximum wait time in seconds. Returns an "
"error if the timeout is reached."
msgstr "`timeout`（float，可选）—— 最大等待时间（秒）。超时时返回错误。"

#: src/languages/python.md:116
msgid ""
"**Returns:** `dict | None` -- An [event dictionary](#event-dictionary), or "
"`None` if all senders have been dropped."
msgstr ""
"**返回：** `dict | None` —— 一个[事件字典](#event-dictionary)，如果所有发送者"
"已被释放则为 `None`。"

#: src/languages/python.md:118
msgid ""
"**Note:** This method is experimental. The pyo3 async (Rust-Python FFI) "
"integration is still in development."
