"node-api-c`（构建为 `staticlib`）"

#: src/languages/c.md:33
msgid ""
"The Node API is used by standalone C executables that participate in an "
"Adora dataflow as external processes. The daemon spawns the process and sets "
"environment variables that the node reads during initialization."
msgstr ""
"节点 API 供作为外部进程参与 Adora 数据流的独立 C 可执行文件使用。守护进程生成"
"进程并设置节点在初始化期间读取的环境变量。"

#: src/languages/c.md:37
msgid "`init_adora_context_from_env`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:43
msgid ""
"Initializes an Adora node context from environment variables set by the "
"daemon. Returns an opaque pointer to the context on success, or `NULL` on "
"failure."
msgstr ""
"从守护进程设置的环境变量初始化 Adora 节点上下文。成功时返回指向上下文的不透明"
"指针，失败时返回 `NULL`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:45
msgid ""
"The returned pointer must be passed to all subsequent Node API calls that "
"expect a context argument. When the node is finished, free it with "
"`free_adora_context`."
msgstr ""
"返回的指针必须传递给所有期望上下文参数的后续节点 API 调用。节点完成后，使用 "
"`free_adora_context` 释放。"

#: src/languages/c.md:47
msgid "`free_adora_context`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:53
msgid ""
"Frees a context previously created by `init_adora_context_from_env`. Each "
"context must be freed exactly once. After freeing, the pointer must not be "
"used again."
msgstr ""
"释放先前由 `init_adora_context_from_env` 创建的上下文。每个上下文必须恰好释放"
"一次。释放后不得再次使用该指针。"

#: src/languages/c.md:55
msgid "Event Loop"
msgstr "事件循环"

#: src/languages/c.md:57
msgid "`adora_next_event`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:63
msgid ""
"Blocks until the next event is available for this node. Returns an opaque "
"pointer to the event, or `NULL` when all event streams have closed "
"(indicating the node should exit)."
msgstr ""
"阻塞直到此节点有可用的下一个事件。返回指向事件的不透明指针，当所有事件流关闭"
"时返回 `NULL`（表示节点应退出）。"

#: src/languages/c.md:65
msgid ""
"The returned pointer must not be dereferenced directly. Use the "
"`read_adora_*` functions to extract the event type and payload. Free the "
"event with `free_adora_event` when done."
msgstr ""
"返回的指针不能直接解引用。使用 `read_adora_*` 函数提取事件类型和载荷。完成后"
"使用 `free_adora_event` 释放事件。"

#: src/languages/c.md:67
msgid "`free_adora_event`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:73
msgid ""
"Frees an event previously returned by `adora_next_event`. Each event must be "
"freed exactly once. After freeing, the event pointer and all derived "
"pointers (from `read_adora_input_id`, `read_adora_input_data`) become "
"invalid."
msgstr ""
"释放先前由 `adora_next_event` 返回的事件。每个事件必须恰好释放一次。释放后，"
"事件指针和所有派生指针（来自 `read_adora_input_id`、`read_adora_input_data`）"
"都将失效。"

#: src/languages/c.md:75
msgid "Event Inspection"
msgstr "事件检查"

#: src/languages/c.md:77
msgid "`read_adora_event_type`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:83
msgid ""
"Returns the type of the given event. See [AdoraEventType](#adoraeventtype) "
"for possible values."
msgstr "返回给定事件的类型。可能的值请参见 [AdoraEventType](#adoraeventtype)。"

#: src/languages/c.md:85
msgid "`read_adora_input_id`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:91
msgid ""
"Reads the input ID from an `AdoraEventType_Input` event. Writes the string "
"start pointer to `*out_ptr` and its byte length to `*out_len`. The string is "
"valid UTF-8 but **not** null-terminated; use `out_len` to determine its "
"bounds."
msgstr ""
"从 `AdoraEventType_Input` 事件读取输入 ID。将字符串起始指针写入 `*out_ptr`，"
"字节长度写入 `*out_len`。字符串是有效的 UTF-8 但**不**以 null 结尾；使用 "
"`out_len` 确定其边界。"

#: src/languages/c.md:93
msgid ""
"If the event is not an input event, sets `*out_ptr = NULL` and `*out_len = "
"0`."
msgstr "如果事件不是输入事件，则设置 `*out_ptr = NULL` 和 `*out_len = 0`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:95 src/languages/c.md:109
msgid ""
"The returned pointer borrows from the event. It becomes invalid after "
"`free_adora_event` is called."
msgstr "返回的指针借用自事件。调用 `free_adora_event` 后将失效。"

#: src/languages/c.md:97
msgid "`read_adora_input_data`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:103
msgid ""
"Reads the raw data bytes from an `AdoraEventType_Input` event. Writes the "
"data start pointer to `*out_ptr` and its byte length to `*out_len`."
msgstr ""
"从 `AdoraEventType_Input` 事件读取原始数据字节。将数据起始指针写入 "
"`*out_ptr`，字节长度写入 `*out_len`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:105
msgid ""
"Sets `*out_ptr = NULL` and `*out_len = 0` if the event is not an input event "
"or the input carries no data."
msgstr ""
"如果事件不是输入事件或输入不携带数据，则设置 `*out_ptr = NULL` 和 `*out_len "
"= 0`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:107
msgid ""
"Currently only `UInt8` Arrow arrays are supported. Other Arrow data types "
"will cause a runtime panic. Future versions will use the Arrow C Data "
"Interface for full type support."
msgstr ""
"目前仅支持 `UInt8` Arrow 数组。其他 Arrow 数据类型会导致运行时 panic。未来版"
"本将使用 Arrow C Data Interface 以支持所有类型。"

#: src/languages/c.md:111
msgid "`read_adora_input_timestamp`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:117
msgid ""
"Returns the hybrid logical clock timestamp from an input event's metadata as "
"a `uint64` value. Returns `0` if the event is not an input event."
msgstr ""
"以 `uint64` 值形式返回输入事件元数据中的混合逻辑时钟时间戳。如果事件不是输入"
"事件则返回 `0`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:119
msgid "Output"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:121
msgid "`adora_send_output`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:133
msgid ""
"Sends output data to all downstream subscribers. The output ID (`id_ptr`/"
"`id_len`) must be a valid UTF-8 string matching one of the node's declared "
"outputs in the dataflow YAML. The data (`data_ptr`/`data_len`) is sent as "
"raw bytes (UInt8 Arrow array)."
msgstr ""
"向所有下游订阅者发送输出数据。输出 ID（`id_ptr`/`id_len`）必须是有效的 UTF-8 "
"字符串，与数据流 YAML 中节点声明的某个输出匹配。数据（`data_ptr`/`data_len`）"
"作为原始字节（UInt8 Arrow 数组）发送。"

#: src/languages/c.md:135
msgid "Returns `0` on success, `-1` on error. Errors are logged via `tracing`."
msgstr "成功返回 `0`，错误返回 `-1`。错误通过 `tracing` 记录。"

#: src/languages/c.md:137
msgid "Returns `-1` immediately if any pointer argument is `NULL`."
msgstr "如果任何指针参数为 `NULL`，则立即返回 `-1`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:141
msgid "`adora_log`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:153
msgid ""
"Sends a structured log message through the Adora logging pipeline. Both "
"`level` and `msg` must be valid UTF-8 strings."
msgstr ""
"通过 Adora 日志管道发送结构化日志消息。`level` 和 `msg` 都必须是有效的 UTF-8 "
"字符串。"

#: src/languages/c.md:155
msgid ""
"Valid log levels: `\"error\"`, `\"warn\"`, `\"info\"`, `\"debug\"`, "
"`\"trace\"`."
msgstr ""
"有效的日志级别：`\"error\"`、`\"warn\"`、`\"info\"`、`\"debug\"`、"
"`\"trace\"`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:157
msgid ""
"Returns `0` on success, `-1` on error. Returns `-1` immediately if any "
"pointer argument is `NULL`."
msgstr ""
"成功返回 `0`，错误返回 `-1`。如果任何指针参数为 `NULL`，则立即返回 `-1`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:159
msgid "Enums"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:161
msgid "`AdoraEventType`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:165
msgid "// Graceful shutdown requested\n"
msgstr "// 请求优雅关闭\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:166
msgid "// New input data available\n"
msgstr "// 有新输入数据可用\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:167
msgid "// An input stream was closed\n"
msgstr "// 输入流已关闭\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:168
msgid "// An error occurred\n"
msgstr "// 发生错误\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:169
msgid "// Unrecognized event type\n"
msgstr "// 无法识别的事件类型\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:175
msgid "Operator API (adora-operator-api-c)"
msgstr "算子 API (adora-operator-api-c)"

#: src/languages/c.md:177
msgid ""
"Headers: [`apis/c/operator/operator_api.h`](../apis/c/operator/"
"operator_api.h), [`apis/c/operator/operator_types.h`](../apis/c/operator/"
"operator_types.h) Crate: `adora-operator-api-c`"
msgstr ""
"头文件：[`apis/c/operator/operator_api.h`](../apis/c/operator/"
"operator_api.h)、[`apis/c/operator/operator_types.h`](../apis/c/operator/"
"operator_types.h) Crate：`adora-operator-api-c`"

#: src/languages/c.md:180
msgid ""
"The Operator API is used by shared libraries (`.so`/`.dylib`/`.dll`) loaded "
"into the Adora runtime process. Unlike nodes, operators do not have their "
"own `main` function. Instead, they export three functions that the runtime "
"calls at the appropriate lifecycle points."
msgstr ""
"算子 API 供加载到 Adora 运行时进程中的共享库（`.so`/`.dylib`/`.dll`）使用。与"
"节点不同，算子没有自己的 `main` 函数。它们导出三个函数，由运行时在适当的生命"
"周期点调用。"

#: src/languages/c.md:182
msgid ""
"The `operator_types.h` header is auto-generated by `safer-ffi` and defines "
"all C-compatible struct and enum types."
msgstr ""
"`operator_types.h` 头文件由 `safer-ffi` 自动生成，定义了所有 C 兼容的结构体和"
"枚举类型。"

#: src/languages/c.md:184
msgid "Lifecycle Functions"
msgstr "生命周期函数"

#: src/languages/c.md:186
msgid "`adora_init_operator`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:192
msgid ""
"Called once when the runtime loads the operator. Allocate and initialize any "
"operator state, then return it via the `operator_context` field. The runtime "
"passes this pointer back on every subsequent call."
msgstr ""
"运行时加载算子时调用一次。分配并初始化所有算子状态，然后通过 "
"`operator_context` 字段返回。运行时在每次后续调用中传回此指针。"

#: src/languages/c.md:194
msgid "Return an `AdoraInitResult_t` with `.result.error = NULL` on success."
msgstr "成功时返回 `.result.error = NULL` 的 `AdoraInitResult_t`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:196
msgid "`adora_drop_operator`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:202
msgid ""
"Called once when the operator is being unloaded. Free all resources "
"associated with `operator_context`."
msgstr "算子被卸载时调用一次。释放与 `operator_context` 关联的所有资源。"

#: src/languages/c.md:204
msgid "Return an `AdoraResult_t` with `.error = NULL` on success."
msgstr "成功时返回 `.error = NULL` 的 `AdoraResult_t`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:206
msgid "Event Handling"
msgstr "事件处理"

#: src/languages/c.md:208
msgid "`adora_on_event`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:218
msgid ""
"Called by the runtime each time an event arrives for this operator. Inspect "
"the `event` fields to determine the event type:"
msgstr "每当此算子有事件到达时由运行时调用。检查 `event` 字段以确定事件类型："

#: src/languages/c.md:222
msgid "`event->input != NULL`"
msgstr "`event->input != NULL`"

#: src/languages/c.md:222
msgid "New input available"
msgstr "有新输入可用"

#: src/languages/c.md:223
msgid "`event->stop == true`"
msgstr "`event->stop == true`"

#: src/languages/c.md:223
msgid "Graceful shutdown requested"
msgstr "请求优雅关闭"

#: src/languages/c.md:224
msgid "`event->error.ptr != NULL`"
msgstr "`event->error.ptr != NULL`"

#: src/languages/c.md:224
msgid "An error occurred (UTF-8 string in `error.ptr`/`error.len`)"
msgstr "发生错误（UTF-8 字符串位于 `error.ptr`/`error.len`）"

#: src/languages/c.md:225
msgid "`event->input_closed.ptr != NULL`"
msgstr "`event->input_closed.ptr != NULL`"

#: src/languages/c.md:225
msgid ""
"An input stream closed (input ID in `input_closed.ptr`/`input_closed.len`)"
msgstr "输入流已关闭（输入 ID 位于 `input_closed.ptr`/`input_closed.len`）"

#: src/languages/c.md:227
msgid ""
"Use `send_output` to emit data to downstream nodes (see "
"`adora_send_operator_output`). Return an `OnEventResult_t` with the "
"appropriate `AdoraStatus_t` to control the operator lifecycle."
msgstr ""
"使用 `send_output` 向下游节点发送数据（见 `adora_send_operator_output`）。返"
"回带有适当 `AdoraStatus_t` 的 `OnEventResult_t` 以控制算子生命周期。"

#: src/languages/c.md:229
msgid "Input Reading"
msgstr "输入读取"

#: src/languages/c.md:231 src/languages/c.md:272
msgid "`adora_read_input_id`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:237
msgid ""
"Returns a newly allocated null-terminated string containing the input ID. "
"The caller must free it with `adora_free_input_id`."
msgstr ""
"返回新分配的以 null 结尾的字符串，包含输入 ID。调用者必须使用 "
"`adora_free_input_id` 释放。"

#: src/languages/c.md:239 src/languages/c.md:273
msgid "`adora_read_data`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:245
msgid ""
"Reads the input data as a byte array. Consumes the underlying Arrow array "
"from the input (the data can only be read once per event). Returns a "
"`Vec_uint8_t` with `.ptr = NULL` if the input has no data or the data has "
"already been consumed."
msgstr ""
"将输入数据作为字节数组读取。从输入中消费底层 Arrow 数组（每个事件只能读取一次"
"数据）。如果输入没有数据或数据已被消费，则返回 `.ptr = NULL` 的 "
"`Vec_uint8_t`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:247
msgid "The caller must free the returned data with `adora_free_data`."
msgstr "调用者必须使用 `adora_free_data` 释放返回的数据。"

#: src/languages/c.md:249
msgid "Output Sending"
msgstr "输出发送"

#: src/languages/c.md:251
msgid "`adora_send_operator_output`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:262
msgid ""
"Sends output data to downstream subscribers. The `id` must be a null-"
"terminated string matching one of the operator's declared outputs. The data "
"(`data_ptr`/`data_len`) is converted to a UInt8 Arrow array internally."
msgstr ""
"向下游订阅者发送输出数据。`id` 必须是以 null 结尾的字符串，与算子声明的某个输"
"出匹配。数据（`data_ptr`/`data_len`）在内部被转换为 UInt8 Arrow 数组。"

#: src/languages/c.md:264
msgid "Returns an `AdoraResult_t` with `.error = NULL` on success."
msgstr "成功时返回 `.error = NULL` 的 `AdoraResult_t`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:266
msgid "Memory Management"
msgstr "内存管理"

#: src/languages/c.md:268
msgid ""
"The Operator API allocates memory that the caller must free using the "
"corresponding functions:"
msgstr "算子 API 分配的内存必须由调用者使用相应的函数释放："

#: src/languages/c.md:270
msgid "Allocation source"
msgstr "分配来源"

#: src/languages/c.md:270
msgid "Free function"
msgstr "释放函数"

#: src/languages/c.md:272
msgid "`adora_free_input_id`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:273
msgid "`adora_free_data`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:280
msgid ""
"Failing to call these functions will leak memory. Do not use `free()` on "
"these allocations -- they are allocated by the Rust runtime and must be "
"freed through the API."
msgstr ""
"不调用这些函数会导致内存泄漏。不要对这些分配使用 `free()`——它们由 Rust 运行时"
"分配，必须通过 API 释放。"

#: src/languages/c.md:282
msgid "Structs"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:284
msgid "`Vec_uint8_t`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:294
msgid ""
"A Rust-allocated byte vector. Access `len` bytes starting at `ptr`. Do not "
"modify `cap`. Free with `adora_free_data`."
msgstr ""
"Rust 分配的字节向量。从 `ptr` 开始访问 `len` 个字节。不要修改 `cap`。使用 "
"`adora_free_data` 释放。"

#: src/languages/c.md:296
msgid "`AdoraResult_t`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:300
msgid "// NULL on success, points to error string on failure\n"
msgstr "// 成功时为 NULL，失败时指向错误字符串\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:304
msgid ""
"Generic result type. A `NULL` error pointer indicates success. When non-"
"NULL, the error pointer contains a UTF-8 error message."
msgstr ""
"通用结果类型。`NULL` 错误指针表示成功。非 NULL 时，错误指针包含 UTF-8 错误消"
"息。"

#: src/languages/c.md:306
msgid "`AdoraInitResult_t`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:311
msgid "// opaque pointer to operator state\n"
msgstr "// 算子状态的不透明指针\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:315
msgid ""
"Returned by `adora_init_operator`. On success, `result.error` is `NULL` and "
"`operator_context` holds the operator state pointer."
msgstr ""
"由 `adora_init_operator` 返回。成功时 `result.error` 为 `NULL`，"
"`operator_context` 持有算子状态指针。"

#: src/languages/c.md:317
msgid "`OnEventResult_t`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:326
msgid ""
"Returned by `adora_on_event`. Contains both an error/success result and a "
"status code controlling the operator lifecycle."
msgstr ""
"由 `adora_on_event` 返回。包含错误/成功结果和控制算子生命周期的状态码。"

#: src/languages/c.md:328
msgid "`RawEvent_t`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:332
msgid "// non-NULL when this is an input event\n"
msgstr "// 输入事件时为非 NULL\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:333
msgid "// non-empty when an input stream closed\n"
msgstr "// 输入流关闭时为非空\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:334
msgid "// true when shutdown is requested\n"
msgstr "// 请求关闭时为 true\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:335
msgid "// non-empty on error\n"
msgstr "// 错误时为非空\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:339
msgid ""
"Represents an event delivered to the operator. Multiple fields may be set "
"simultaneously; check them in order of priority."
msgstr "表示传递给算子的事件。多个字段可能同时被设置；按优先级顺序检查它们。"

#: src/languages/c.md:341
msgid "`Input_t`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:344 src/languages/c.md:352
msgid "// opaque\n"
msgstr "// 不透明\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:347
msgid ""
"Opaque type representing an input event's data. Use `adora_read_input_id` "
"and `adora_read_data` to extract its contents."
msgstr ""
"表示输入事件数据的不透明类型。使用 `adora_read_input_id` 和 "
"`adora_read_data` 提取其内容。"

#: src/languages/c.md:349
msgid "`Output_t`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:355
msgid ""
"Opaque type used internally by `adora_send_operator_output`. Not created "
"directly by user code."
msgstr ""
"由 `adora_send_operator_output` 内部使用的不透明类型。不由用户代码直接创建。"

#: src/languages/c.md:357
msgid "`SendOutput_t`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:365
msgid ""
"Callback handle passed to `adora_on_event`. Pass it to "
"`adora_send_operator_output` to emit data. Do not store it beyond the scope "
"of the current `adora_on_event` call."
msgstr ""
"传递给 `adora_on_event` 的回调句柄。将其传递给 `adora_send_operator_output` "
"以发送数据。不要将其存储在当前 `adora_on_event` 调用的范围之外。"

#: src/languages/c.md:367
msgid "`Metadata_t`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:375
msgid "Event metadata containing an OpenTelemetry trace context string."
msgstr "包含 OpenTelemetry 追踪上下文字符串的事件元数据。"

#: src/languages/c.md:377
msgid "Operator Enums"
msgstr "算子枚举"

#: src/languages/c.md:379
msgid "`AdoraStatus_t`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:383
msgid "// Keep running\n"
msgstr "// 继续运行\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:384
msgid "// Stop this operator\n"
msgstr "// 停止此算子\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:385
msgid "// Stop the entire dataflow\n"
msgstr "// 停止整个数据流\n"

#: src/languages/c.md:390
msgid ""
"Returned in `OnEventResult_t` to control operator lifecycle after processing "
"an event."
msgstr "在 `OnEventResult_t` 中返回，用于在处理事件后控制算子生命周期。"

#: src/languages/c.md:394
msgid "Node Example"
msgstr "节点示例"

#: src/languages/c.md:396
msgid "A complete C node that receives timer ticks and sends output messages:"
msgstr "一个接收定时器 tick 并发送输出消息的完整 C 节点："

#: src/languages/c.md:399
msgid "<stdio.h>"
msgstr ""

