msgid "CXX Bridge Notes"
msgstr "CXX 桥接注意事项"

#: src/languages/cpp.md:637
msgid ""
"All Rust opaque types (`Events`, `OutputSender`, `AdoraEvent`, `Metadata`, "
"`MergedEvents`, `MergedAdoraEvent`) are accessed through `rust::Box<T>`."
msgstr ""
"所有 Rust 不透明类型（`Events`、`OutputSender`、`AdoraEvent`、`Metadata`、"
"`MergedEvents`、`MergedAdoraEvent`）通过 `rust::Box<T>` 访问。"

#: src/languages/cpp.md:638
msgid ""
"`rust::String`, `rust::Vec<T>`, and `rust::Slice<const T>` are CXX bridge "
"types that interoperate with their C++ standard library counterparts. See "
"the [CXX type reference](https://cxx.rs/binding/box.html)."
msgstr ""
"`rust::String`、`rust::Vec<T>` 和 `rust::Slice<const T>` 是 CXX 桥接类型，与"
"对应的 C++ 标准库类型互操作。参见 [CXX 类型参考](https://cxx.rs/binding/"
"box.html)。"

#: src/languages/cpp.md:639
msgid ""
"Functions that return `Result<T>` in Rust throw C++ exceptions on the error "
"path."
msgstr "在 Rust 中返回 `Result<T>` 的函数在错误路径上抛出 C++ 异常。"

#: src/languages/cpp.md:640
msgid ""
"Arrow FFI functions (`event_as_arrow_input`, `send_arrow_output`) are "
"`unsafe` on the Rust side. The caller must pass valid pointers to "
"`ArrowArray` / `ArrowSchema` structs cast to `uint8_t*`."
msgstr ""
"Arrow FFI 函数（`event_as_arrow_input`、`send_arrow_output`）在 Rust 侧是 "
"`unsafe` 的。调用者必须传递转换为 `uint8_t*` 的有效 `ArrowArray` / "
"`ArrowSchema` 结构体指针。"

#: src/languages/cpp.md:641
msgid ""
"The node library is a static archive (`staticlib`). Link it into your "
"executable with `-ladora_node_api_cxx`."
msgstr ""
"节点库是静态归档（`staticlib`）。使用 `-ladora_node_api_cxx` 将其链接到你的可"
"执行文件。"

#: src/languages/cpp.md:642
msgid ""
"The operator library is also a static archive. Link it into your shared "
"library with `-ladora_operator_api_cxx`."
msgstr ""
"算子库也是静态归档。使用 `-ladora_operator_api_cxx` 将其链接到你的共享库。"

