#: src/operations/cli.md:74
msgid ""
"A **dataflow** is a directed graph of nodes connected by typed data "
"channels. Nodes produce **outputs** that other nodes consume as **inputs**. "
"The framework handles data routing, serialization (Apache Arrow), and "
"lifecycle management."
msgstr ""
"**数据流**是由类型化数据通道连接的节点有向图。节点产生**输出**，其他节点将其"
"作为**输入**消费。框架负责数据路由、序列化（Apache Arrow）和生命周期管理。"

