#: src/operations/cli.md:343
msgid ""
"**Type checking:** After expanding modules, `build` runs the same type "
"checks as `validate`. Warnings are printed by default; use `--strict-types` "
"(or set `strict_types: true` in the YAML) to fail the build on type "
"mismatches. User-defined types in a `types/` directory next to the dataflow "
"are loaded automatically."
msgstr ""

#: src/operations/cli.md:345
msgid ""
"**Build strategy:** If nodes have `_unstable_deploy` sections and a "
"coordinator is reachable, builds are distributed to target machines. "
"Otherwise, builds run locally."
msgstr ""
