"标机器。否则在本地构建。"

#: src/operations/cli.md:347
msgid ""
"**Git sources:** Nodes with a `git:` field are cloned/updated before "
"building. The build command runs from the git repository root."
msgstr ""
"**Git 源：**带有 `git:` 字段的节点在构建前会被克隆/更新。构建命令从 git 仓库"
"根目录运行。"

