#: src/operations/logging.md:136
msgid "How Node Output Becomes Log Entries"
msgstr "节点输出如何变为日志条目"

#: src/operations/logging.md:138
msgid ""
"The daemon captures each line of stdout/stderr from a node process and "
"attempts to parse it as a structured log message (JSON with `level`, "
"`message`, `timestamp`, and optional `fields`). If parsing succeeds, the "
"structured fields are preserved. If parsing fails, the raw line becomes a "
"`\"stdout\"`\\-level entry."
msgstr ""
"守护进程捕获节点进程的每行 stdout/stderr 并尝试将其解析为结构化日志消息（包"
"含 `level`、`message`、`timestamp` 和可选 `fields` 的 JSON）。解析成功时保留"
"结构化字段。解析失败时，原始行变为 `\"stdout\"`\\-level 条目。"

#: src/operations/logging.md:140
msgid ""
"This means nodes using Rust's `tracing` or `log` crate with JSON output get "
"full structured logging automatically. Nodes that simply `println!` produce "
"`\"stdout\"`\\-level entries."
msgstr ""
"这意味着使用 Rust 的 `tracing` 或 `log` crate 并输出 JSON 的节点会自动获得完"
"整的结构化日志。仅使用 `println!` 的节点则产生 `\"stdout\"`\\-level 条目。"

#: src/operations/logging.md:144
msgid "Viewing Logs: `adora run`"
msgstr "查看日志：`adora run`"

