#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:277
msgid "Internal Design"
msgstr "内部设计"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:279
msgid "`InputTracker` maintains two `HashMap`s:"
msgstr "`InputTracker` 维护两个 `HashMap`："

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:281
msgid ""
"`states: HashMap<DataId, InputState>` -- current state per input (Healthy or "
"Closed)"
msgstr ""
"`states: HashMap<DataId, InputState>` —— 每个输入的当前状态（Healthy 或 "
"Closed）"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:282
msgid "`cache: HashMap<DataId, ArrowData>` -- last received value per input"
msgstr "`cache: HashMap<DataId, ArrowData>` —— 每个输入最后接收到的值"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:284
msgid ""
"On `Event::Input`, both maps are updated (state = Healthy, cache = data "
"clone). On `Event::InputClosed`, only state changes (cache is preserved). On "
"`Event::InputRecovered`, state is set back to Healthy. The cache is never "
"cleared, so `last_value()` always returns the most recent data even after "
"the input closes."
msgstr ""
"收到 `Event::Input` 时，两个映射都会更新（状态 = Healthy，缓存 = 数据克隆）。"
"收到 `Event::InputClosed` 时，仅状态变化（缓存保留）。收到 "
"`Event::InputRecovered` 时，状态恢复为 Healthy。缓存永远不会被清除，因此 "
"`last_value()` 即使在输入关闭后也始终返回最近的数据。"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:286
msgid ""
"Note: `ArrowData` wraps `Arc<dyn arrow::array::Array>`, so the cache clone "
"is reference-counted (cheap)."
msgstr ""
"注意：`ArrowData` 包装了 `Arc<dyn arrow::array::Array>`，因此缓存克隆是引用计"
"数的（低开销）。"

