#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:365
msgid "Coordinator State Persistence"
msgstr "协调器状态持久化"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:367
msgid ""
"By default the coordinator holds all state in memory. If the coordinator "
"process crashes or is restarted, all knowledge of running dataflows is lost "
"-- daemons continue running but become orphaned, and users must manually re-"
"run dataflows."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，协调器将所有状态保存在内存中。如果协调器进程崩溃或重启，所有运行"
"中数据流的信息都会丢失——守护进程继续运行但成为孤立状态，用户必须手动重新运行"
"数据流。"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:369
msgid ""
"The **redb store backend** solves this by persisting coordinator state to a "
"single file on disk using [redb](https://docs.rs/redb), a pure-Rust embedded "
"key-value store with copy-on-write B-trees that are crash-safe by design."
msgstr ""
"**redb 存储后端**通过使用 [redb](https://docs.rs/redb) 将协调器状态持久化到磁"
"盘上的单个文件来解决这个问题。redb 是一个纯 Rust 嵌入式键值存储，采用写时复"
"制 B 树，设计上具有崩溃安全性。"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:371
msgid "Design: Stateless Coordinator with Stateful Backend"
msgstr "设计：无状态协调器与有状态后端"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:373
msgid ""
"The coordinator itself remains stateless in the K8s sense -- it can be "
"stopped and restarted at any time. All durable state lives in the store "
"backend behind the `CoordinatorStore` trait:"
msgstr ""
"协调器本身在 K8s 意义上保持无状态——它可以随时停止和重启。所有持久状态存储在 "
"`CoordinatorStore` trait 背后的存储后端中："

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:385
msgid "This separation means:"
msgstr "这种分离意味着："

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:386
msgid ""
"The coordinator event loop never reads from the filesystem during normal "
"operation (only at startup recovery)"
msgstr "协调器事件循环在正常运行期间从不读取文件系统（仅在启动恢复时）"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:387
msgid ""
"All state mutations are written to the store at well-defined persistence "
"points"
msgstr "所有状态变更在明确定义的持久化点写入存储"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:388
msgid "The store can be swapped without changing coordinator logic"
msgstr "可以在不改变协调器逻辑的情况下更换存储"

