msgstr "递增 generation 计数器"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:452
msgid "Write the updated record back to the store"
msgstr "将更新后的记录写回存储"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:453
msgid "Terminal records (`Succeeded`, `Failed`) are left unchanged"
msgstr "终态记录（`Succeeded`、`Failed`）保持不变"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:455
msgid ""
