"confused with actively running ones. The daemons that were running those "
"dataflows will detect the coordinator disconnect independently."
msgstr ""
"这确保了崩溃的协调器遗留的过期数据流不会与正在运行的数据流混淆。运行这些数据"
"流的守护进程将独立检测到协调器断开。"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:457
