#: src/operations/distributed.md:34
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:36
msgid "Adora's distributed architecture has three tiers:"
msgstr "Adora 的分布式架构有三个层级："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:43
msgid "**CLI** sends control commands (build, start, stop) to the coordinator."
msgstr "**CLI** 向协调器发送控制命令（构建、启动、停止）。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:44
msgid ""
"**Coordinator** orchestrates daemons, resolves node placement, and manages "
"dataflow lifecycle."
msgstr "**协调器**编排守护进程、解析节点放置、管理数据流生命周期。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:45
msgid ""
"**Daemons** run on each machine, spawning and supervising node processes."
msgstr "**守护进程**在每台机器上运行，生成和监控节点进程。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:46
msgid ""
"**Nodes** communicate via shared memory (same machine) or Zenoh pub-sub "
"(cross-machine)."
msgstr "**节点**通过共享内存（同一机器）或 Zenoh 发布/订阅（跨机器）通信。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:48
msgid "There are two paths to distributed deployment:"
msgstr "分布式部署有两种路径："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:50
msgid ""
"**Ad-hoc** -- manually start `adora daemon` on each machine, then use the "
"coordinator for control. Good for development and testing. See [Distributed "
"Deployments in the CLI reference](cli.md#distributed-deployments)."
msgstr ""
"**临时部署** —— 在每台机器上手动启动 `adora daemon`，然后使用协调器进行控制。"
"适合开发和测试。参见 [CLI 参考中的分布式部署](cli.md#distributed-"
"deployments)。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:52
msgid ""
"**Managed (cluster.yml)** -- define your cluster topology in a YAML file, "
"then use `adora cluster` commands for SSH-based lifecycle management. This "
"guide focuses on the managed path."
msgstr ""
"**托管部署 (cluster.yml)** —— 在 YAML 文件中定义集群拓扑，然后使用 `adora "
"cluster` 命令进行基于 SSH 的生命周期管理。本指南重点介绍托管路径。"

