"从每台机器卸载 adora-daemon systemd 服务。停止、禁用并移除 systemd 单元。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:316
msgid "For each machine, runs:"
msgstr "对每台机器运行："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:325
msgid "adora cluster upgrade"
msgstr "adora cluster upgrade"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:327
msgid ""
"Rolling upgrade: SCP the local `adora` binary to each machine and restart "
"daemons. Processes machines sequentially to maintain availability."
msgstr ""
"滚动升级：通过 SCP 将本地 `adora` 二进制文件传输到每台机器并重启守护进程。按"
"顺序处理机器以保持可用性。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:335
msgid "For each machine sequentially:"
msgstr "对每台机器按顺序执行："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:337
msgid ""
"SCP the local `adora` binary to `/usr/local/bin/adora` on the target machine."
msgstr ""
"通过 SCP 将本地 `adora` 二进制文件传输到目标机器的 `/usr/local/bin/adora`。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:338
msgid ""
"Restart the systemd service via `sudo systemctl restart adora-daemon-<id>`."
msgstr "通过 `sudo systemctl restart adora-daemon-<id>` 重启 systemd 服务。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:339
msgid ""
"Poll the coordinator until the daemon reconnects (30s timeout, 500ms "
"intervals)."
msgstr "轮询协调器直到守护进程重新连接（30 秒超时，500 毫秒间隔）。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:341
msgid ""
"Nodes on other machines continue running while each machine is being "
"upgraded."
msgstr "在每台机器升级期间，其他机器上的节点继续运行。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:358
msgid "adora cluster restart"
msgstr "adora cluster restart"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:360
msgid ""
"Restart a running dataflow by name or UUID. Stops the dataflow and "
"immediately re-starts it using the stored descriptor (no YAML path needed)."
msgstr ""
"按名称或 UUID 重启运行中的数据流。停止数据流并立即使用存储的描述符重新启动"
"（不需要 YAML 路径）。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:370
msgid "`DATAFLOW`"
msgstr ""

#: src/operations/distributed.md:370
msgid "Name or UUID of the dataflow to restart"
msgstr "要重启的数据流的名称或 UUID"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:382
msgid "Node Scheduling"
msgstr "节点调度"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:384
msgid ""
"When the coordinator receives a dataflow, it decides which daemon runs each "
"node based on the `_unstable_deploy` section in the dataflow YAML. "
"Resolution priority: **machine > labels > unnamed**."
msgstr ""
"当协调器收到数据流时，它根据数据流 YAML 中的 `_unstable_deploy` 部分决定哪个"
"守护进程运行每个节点。解析优先级：**machine > labels > unnamed**。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:386
msgid "Machine-based scheduling"
msgstr "基于机器的调度"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:388
msgid "Assign a node to a specific machine by its `id` from `cluster.yml`:"
msgstr "通过 `cluster.yml` 中的 `id` 将节点分配到特定机器："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:400
msgid ""
"The coordinator looks up the daemon whose `machine-id` matches. If no "
"matching daemon is connected, the deployment fails with: `no matching daemon "
"for machine id \"robot\"`."
msgstr ""
"协调器查找 `machine-id` 匹配的守护进程。如果没有匹配的守护进程连接，部署将失"
"败并提示：`no matching daemon for machine id \"robot\"`。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:402
msgid "Label-based scheduling"
msgstr "基于标签的调度"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:404
msgid "Assign a node by requiring specific labels on the target daemon:"
msgstr "通过要求目标守护进程具有特定标签来分配节点："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:419
msgid ""
"The coordinator finds the first connected daemon whose labels are a "
"**superset** of the required labels. All required key-value pairs must match "
"exactly. If no daemon satisfies the requirements, deployment fails with: `no "
"daemon matches labels {\"gpu\": \"true\"}`."
msgstr ""
"协调器查找第一个标签是所需标签**超集**的已连接守护进程。所有必需的键值对必须"
"完全匹配。如果没有守护进程满足要求，部署将失败并提示：`no daemon matches "
"labels {\"gpu\": \"true\"}`。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:421
msgid "Unassigned nodes"
msgstr "未分配的节点"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:423
msgid ""
"Nodes without an `_unstable_deploy` section (or with an empty one) are "
"assigned to the first unnamed daemon -- one that connected without a `--"
"machine-id` flag."
msgstr ""
"没有 `_unstable_deploy` 部分（或该部分为空）的节点被分配到第一个未命名的守护"
"进程——即未使用 `--machine-id` 标志连接的守护进程。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:425
msgid "How resolve_daemon() works internally"
msgstr "resolve_daemon() 的内部工作原理"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:427
msgid "The coordinator resolves node placement in `coordinator/run/mod.rs`:"
msgstr "协调器在 `coordinator/run/mod.rs` 中解析节点放置："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:439
msgid ""
"The label matching function iterates over all connected daemons and checks "
"that every required key-value pair exists in the daemon's label set "
"(`conn.labels.get(k) == Some(v)`). This is a superset check: a daemon with "
"`{gpu: \"true\", arch: \"arm64\", role: \"edge\"}` satisfies the requirement "
"`{gpu: \"true\"}`."
msgstr ""
"标签匹配函数遍历所有已连接的守护进程，检查每个必需的键值对是否存在于守护进程"
"的标签集中（`conn.labels.get(k) == Some(v)`）。这是一个超集检查：具有 `{gpu: "
"\"true\", arch: \"arm64\", role: \"edge\"}` 的守护进程满足 `{gpu: \"true\"}` "
"的要求。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:443
msgid "Binary Distribution"
msgstr "二进制分发"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:445
msgid ""
"Control how node binaries are delivered to remote daemons via the "
"`distribute` field."
msgstr "通过 `distribute` 字段控制节点二进制文件如何交付到远程守护进程。"

