msgstr "需要所有守护进程能访问协调器"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:498
msgid "systemd Service Management"
msgstr "systemd 服务管理"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:500
msgid ""
"For production deployments, install daemons as systemd services so they "
"survive reboots and auto-restart on failure."
msgstr ""
"对于生产部署，将守护进程安装为 systemd 服务，使其在重启后存活并在故障时自动重"
"启。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:502
msgid "Install"
msgstr ""

#: src/operations/distributed.md:508
msgid ""
"Creates a systemd unit file on each machine (see [adora cluster install]"
"(#adora-cluster-install) for the full unit template). Key properties:"
msgstr ""
"在每台机器上创建 systemd 单元文件（完整单元模板见 [adora cluster install]"
"(#adora-cluster-install)）。关键属性："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:510
msgid ""
"**Restart=on-failure** with **RestartSec=5**: daemon auto-restarts if it "
"crashes."
msgstr "**Restart=on-failure** 配合 **RestartSec=5**：守护进程崩溃时自动重启。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:511
msgid "**After=network-online.target**: waits for network before starting."
msgstr "**After=network-online.target**：启动前等待网络就绪。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:512
msgid "**WantedBy=multi-user.target**: starts on boot."
msgstr "**WantedBy=multi-user.target**：开机启动。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:514
msgid "Uninstall"
msgstr ""

#: src/operations/distributed.md:520
msgid ""
"Stops, disables, and removes the unit file from each machine, then reloads "
"the systemd daemon."
msgstr "停止、禁用并从每台机器移除单元文件，然后重新加载 systemd 守护进程。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:522
msgid "Verifying service status"
msgstr "验证服务状态"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:524
msgid "After install, check services directly:"
msgstr "安装后，直接检查服务："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:532
msgid "Auto-Recovery"
msgstr "自动恢复"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:534
msgid ""
"When a daemon disconnects and reconnects (e.g., after a network blip, "
"machine reboot, or service restart), the coordinator automatically re-spawns "
"any missing dataflows on that daemon."
msgstr ""
"当守护进程断开并重新连接时（例如网络闪断、机器重启或服务重启后），协调器自动"
"在该守护进程上重新生成所有缺失的数据流。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:536
msgid "How it works"
msgstr "工作原理"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:538
msgid ""
"Daemon reconnects and sends a `StatusReport` listing its currently running "
"dataflows."
msgstr "守护进程重新连接并发送 `StatusReport`，列出当前运行的数据流。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:539
msgid ""
"Coordinator compares the report against its expected state (dataflows that "
"should have nodes on this daemon)."
msgstr "协调器将报告与其预期状态（应在此守护进程上有节点的数据流）进行比较。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:540
msgid ""
"For each running dataflow with nodes assigned to this daemon that the daemon "
"did not report, the coordinator sends a `SpawnDataflowNodes` command to re-"
"spawn the missing nodes."
msgstr ""
"对于分配到此守护进程但守护进程未报告的每个运行中数据流，协调器发送 "
"`SpawnDataflowNodes` 命令以重新生成缺失的节点。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:542
msgid "30-second backoff"
msgstr "30 秒退避"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:544
msgid ""
"To prevent crash loops (e.g., a node that immediately crashes on spawn), "
"recovery uses a per-daemon, per-dataflow backoff:"
msgstr ""
"为防止崩溃循环（例如节点在生成时立即崩溃），恢复使用每守护进程、每数据流的退"
"避："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:546
msgid "After a recovery attempt, the coordinator records the timestamp."
msgstr "恢复尝试后，协调器记录时间戳。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:547
msgid ""
"Subsequent recovery for the same daemon/dataflow pair is skipped until 30 "
"seconds have elapsed."
msgstr "同一守护进程/数据流对的后续恢复在 30 秒过去之前被跳过。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:548
msgid ""
"The backoff clears when the daemon reports the dataflow as running again."
msgstr "当守护进程报告数据流再次运行时，退避清除。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:550
msgid ""
"This means a node that crashes immediately will only be re-spawned once "
"every 30 seconds, not in a tight loop."
msgstr "这意味着立即崩溃的节点只会每 30 秒重新生成一次，而不是紧密循环。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:552
msgid "Limitations"
msgstr "限制"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:554
msgid ""
"Auto-recovery only applies to dataflows started via `adora start` "
"(coordinator-managed). Local `adora run` dataflows are not tracked by the "
"coordinator."
msgstr ""
"自动恢复仅适用于通过 `adora start` 启动的数据流（协调器管理的）。本地 `adora "
"run` 数据流不受协调器跟踪。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:555
msgid ""
"Recovery re-spawns all nodes assigned to the reconnecting daemon, not "
"individual nodes. For per-node restart on crash, use [restart policies]"
"(fault-tolerance.md#restart-policies)."
msgstr ""
"恢复会重新生成分配到重新连接的守护进程的所有节点，而非单个节点。对于节点崩溃"
"时的单节点重启，请使用[重启策略](fault-tolerance.md#restart-policies)。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:559
msgid "Rolling Upgrade"
msgstr "滚动升级"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:561
msgid ""
"Upgrade the `adora` binary on all cluster machines with zero downtime using "
"sequential per-machine upgrades."
msgstr ""
"使用逐台机器顺序升级，以零停机时间升级所有集群机器上的 `adora` 二进制文件。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:563
msgid "Process"
msgstr ""

#: src/operations/distributed.md:569
msgid "For each machine, sequentially:"
msgstr "对每台机器按顺序执行："

#: src/operations/distributed.md:571
msgid ""
"**SCP** the local `adora` binary to `/usr/local/bin/adora` on the target."
msgstr ""
"**SCP** 将本地 `adora` 二进制文件传输到目标机器的 `/usr/local/bin/adora`。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:572
msgid ""
"**Restart** the systemd service (`systemctl restart adora-daemon-<id>`)."
msgstr "**重启** systemd 服务（`systemctl restart adora-daemon-<id>`）。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:573
msgid "**Poll** the coordinator until the daemon reconnects (30s timeout)."
msgstr "**轮询**协调器直到守护进程重新连接（30 秒超时）。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:575
msgid ""
"Because machines are upgraded one at a time, nodes on other machines "
"continue running. After the daemon reconnects, auto-recovery re-spawns any "
"dataflow nodes that were running on that machine."
msgstr ""
"由于机器逐台升级，其他机器上的节点继续运行。守护进程重新连接后，自动恢复会重"
"新生成在该机器上运行的所有数据流节点。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:579
msgid ""
"Daemons must be installed as systemd services (`adora cluster install`)."
msgstr "守护进程必须已安装为 systemd 服务（`adora cluster install`）。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:580
msgid ""
"The local `adora` binary must be compatible with the cluster's coordinator "
"version."
msgstr "本地 `adora` 二进制文件必须与集群的协调器版本兼容。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:581
msgid "SSH access with `sudo` permissions on all target machines."
msgstr "所有目标机器上具有 `sudo` 权限的 SSH 访问。"

