#: src/operations/distributed.md:761
msgid "Build or download the new `adora` binary locally."
msgstr "在本地构建或下载新的 `adora` 二进制文件。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:762
msgid "Run `adora cluster upgrade cluster.yml`."
msgstr "运行 `adora cluster upgrade cluster.yml`。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:763
msgid "Verify with `adora cluster status` that all daemons reconnected."
msgstr "使用 `adora cluster status` 验证所有守护进程已重新连接。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:764
msgid "Running dataflows are automatically re-spawned via auto-recovery."
msgstr "运行中的数据流通过自动恢复机制自动重新生成。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:768
msgid "**Daemon not connecting**"
msgstr "**守护进程未连接**"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:770
msgid ""
"Verify the coordinator is running and reachable: `curl http://<addr>:6013/"
"api/health` (or check coordinator logs)."
msgstr ""
"验证协调器正在运行且可访问：`curl http://<addr>:6013/api/health`（或检查协调"
"器日志）。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:771
msgid ""
"Check daemon logs: `journalctl -u adora-daemon-<id> -f` (systemd) or the "
"daemon's stderr output (ad-hoc)."
msgstr ""
"检查守护进程日志：`journalctl -u adora-daemon-<id> -f`（systemd）或守护进程"
"的 stderr 输出（临时部署）。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:772
msgid ""
"Confirm the `--coordinator-addr` and `--coordinator-port` match the "
"coordinator's actual bind address."
msgstr ""
"确认 `--coordinator-addr` 和 `--coordinator-port` 与协调器的实际绑定地址匹"
"配。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:774
msgid "**SSH failures during cluster commands**"
msgstr "**集群命令期间的 SSH 失败**"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:776
msgid ""
"Ensure `ssh -o BatchMode=yes <user>@<host> echo ok` works from the CLI "
"machine."
msgstr ""
"确保从 CLI 机器可以成功执行 `ssh -o BatchMode=yes <user>@<host> echo ok`。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:777
msgid ""
"Check that `StrictHostKeyChecking=accept-new` is acceptable for your "
"environment (first connection auto-accepts the host key)."
msgstr ""
"检查 `StrictHostKeyChecking=accept-new` 对你的环境是否可接受（首次连接自动接"
"受主机密钥）。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:778
msgid ""
"Verify the `user` field in `cluster.yml` matches a valid SSH user on the "
"target."
msgstr "验证 `cluster.yml` 中的 `user` 字段与目标机器上的有效 SSH 用户匹配。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:780
msgid "**Label mismatch errors**"
msgstr "**标签不匹配错误**"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:782
msgid "Error: `no daemon matches labels {\"gpu\": \"true\"}`."
msgstr "错误：`no daemon matches labels {\"gpu\": \"true\"}`。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:783
msgid "Check that the daemon was started with the correct `--labels` flag."
msgstr "检查守护进程是否使用了正确的 `--labels` 标志启动。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:784
msgid ""
"Run `adora cluster status` to see connected daemons. Labels are set at "
"daemon startup from `cluster.yml` and cannot be changed at runtime."
msgstr ""
"运行 `adora cluster status` 查看已连接的守护进程。标签在守护进程启动时从 "
"`cluster.yml` 设置，运行时无法更改。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:786
msgid "**Auto-recovery not triggering**"
msgstr "**自动恢复未触发**"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:788
msgid ""
"Auto-recovery only applies to coordinator-managed dataflows (`adora start`), "
"not `adora run`."
msgstr ""
"自动恢复仅适用于协调器管理的数据流（`adora start`），不适用于 `adora run`。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:789
msgid "Check coordinator logs for `auto-recovery: re-spawning` messages."
msgstr "检查协调器日志中的 `auto-recovery: re-spawning` 消息。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:790
msgid ""
"If the node crashes immediately, recovery is throttled to once every 30 "
"seconds per daemon per dataflow."
msgstr "如果节点立即崩溃，恢复被限制为每个守护进程每个数据流每 30 秒一次。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:794
msgid "Deployment YAML Reference"
msgstr "部署 YAML 参考"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:796
msgid ""
"The `_unstable_deploy` section on each node controls placement and "
"distribution. All fields are optional."
msgstr ""
"每个节点上的 `_unstable_deploy` 部分控制放置和分发。所有字段都是可选的。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:802
msgid ""
"edge-01                # Target machine ID from cluster.yml\n"
"      labels"
msgstr ""
"edge-01                # 来自 cluster.yml 的目标机器 ID\n"
"      labels"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:803
msgid ""
"# Label requirements (superset match)\n"
"        gpu"
msgstr ""

#: src/operations/distributed.md:806
msgid ""
"local                # local | scp | http\n"
"      working_dir"
msgstr ""
"local                # local | scp | http\n"
"      working_dir"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:807
msgid ""
"/opt/my-app         # Working directory on the target machine\n"
"    path"
msgstr ""
"/opt/my-app         # 目标机器上的工作目录\n"
"    path"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:815
msgid "Target machine ID. Takes priority over labels."
msgstr "目标机器 ID。优先于标签。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:816
msgid "Required daemon labels. All key-value pairs must match."
msgstr "必需的守护进程标签。所有键值对必须匹配。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:817
msgid "Binary distribution strategy: `local`, `scp`, or `http`."
msgstr "二进制分发策略：`local`、`scp` 或 `http`。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:818
msgid "Working directory on the target machine."
msgstr "目标机器上的工作目录。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:820
msgid "Resolution priority"
msgstr "解析优先级"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:822
msgid ""
"**machine** -- if set, the node is assigned to the daemon with that machine "
"ID."
msgstr "**machine** —— 如果设置，节点被分配到具有该机器 ID 的守护进程。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:823
msgid ""
"**labels** -- if set (and machine is not), the node is assigned to the first "
"daemon whose labels are a superset of the required labels."
msgstr ""
"**labels** —— 如果设置（且未设置 machine），节点被分配到标签是所需标签超集的"
"第一个守护进程。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:824
msgid ""
"**Fallback** -- if neither is set, the node is assigned to the first unnamed "
"(no machine-id) daemon."
msgstr ""
"**回退** —— 如果两者都未设置，节点被分配到第一个未命名（无 machine-id）的守护"
"进程。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:830
msgid ""
"**Use labels over machine IDs** for flexibility. Labels decouple your "
"dataflow from specific machines, making it easier to add, remove, or replace "
"hardware."
msgstr ""
"**优先使用标签而非机器 ID** 以获得灵活性。标签将数据流与特定机器解耦，使添"
"加、移除或替换硬件更容易。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:831
msgid ""
"**Use systemd install for production**. Daemon services survive reboots and "
"auto-restart on failure with `Restart=on-failure`."
msgstr ""
"**生产环境使用 systemd 安装**。守护进程服务在重启后存活，并通过 `Restart=on-"
"failure` 在故障时自动重启。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:832
msgid ""
"**Use coordinator persistence** (`adora coordinator --store redb`) with "
"clusters so the coordinator survives restarts. See [Coordinator State "
"Persistence](fault-tolerance.md#coordinator-state-persistence)."
msgstr ""
"**在集群中使用协调器持久化**（`adora coordinator --store redb`），使协调器在"
"重启后存活。参见[协调器状态持久化](fault-tolerance.md#coordinator-state-"
"persistence)。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:833
msgid ""
"**Set restart policies on nodes** for per-node resilience. Combine with auto-"
"recovery for defense in depth. See [Restart Policies](fault-"
"tolerance.md#restart-policies)."
msgstr ""
"**在节点上设置重启策略**以实现每节点弹性。与自动恢复结合实现纵深防御。参见[重"
"启策略](fault-tolerance.md#restart-policies)。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:834
msgid ""
"**Monitor with multiple tools**: `adora cluster status` for daemon health, "
"`adora top` for resource usage, `adora logs` for node output."
msgstr ""
"**使用多种工具监控**：`adora cluster status` 查看守护进程健康状态，`adora "
"top` 查看资源使用，`adora logs` 查看节点输出。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:835
msgid ""
"**Test locally first**. Develop with `adora run dataflow.yml`, then deploy "
"to a cluster. The same dataflow YAML works in both modes -- "
"`_unstable_deploy` fields are ignored in local mode."
msgstr ""
"**先在本地测试**。使用 `adora run dataflow.yml` 开发，然后部署到集群。相同的"
"数据流 YAML 在两种模式下都有效——`_unstable_deploy` 字段在本地模式下被忽略。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:836
msgid ""
"**Use rolling upgrades** instead of stopping the entire cluster. `adora "
"cluster upgrade` processes one machine at a time to maintain availability."
msgstr ""
"**使用滚动升级**而非停止整个集群。`adora cluster upgrade` 每次处理一台机器以"
"保持可用性。"

#: src/operations/distributed.md:837
msgid ""
"**Keep cluster.yml in version control** alongside your dataflow definitions."
msgstr "**将 cluster.yml 与数据流定义一起纳入版本控制**。"

