"The handler node **must include the same `request_id`** in metadata when "
"sending the response. The simplest approach is to pass through "
"`metadata.parameters`:"
msgstr ""
"每个传入的 ROS2 请求被分配一个 `request_id` 元数据参数。处理节点在发送响应时"
"**必须在元数据中包含相同的 `request_id`**。最简单的方法是直接传递 "
"`metadata.parameters`："

