#: src/advanced/ws-control.md:422
msgid ""
"**Poll-with-timeout**: Integration tests poll coordinator state (e.g., "
"`DaemonConnected`) with a 2-second deadline and 20ms sleep intervals, "
"avoiding flaky timing assumptions."
msgstr ""
"**轮询超时机制**：集成测试通过轮询协调器状态（例如 `DaemonConnected`），设置 "
"2 秒截止时间和 20 毫秒休眠间隔，避免不稳定的时序假设。"

#: src/advanced/ws-control.md:424
msgid ""
"**No nested runtimes**: E2E tests run the coordinator on a background "
"`std::thread` with its own tokio runtime, while `WsSession` (which creates "
"its own current-thread runtime) runs on the test's main thread. This avoids "
"the \"cannot start a runtime from within a runtime\" panic."
msgstr ""
"**禁止嵌套运行时**：端到端测试在后台 `std::thread` 上运行协调器并使用独立的 "
"tokio 运行时，而 `WsSession`（会创建自己的当前线程运行时）则在测试主线程上运"
"行。这样可以避免 \"cannot start a runtime from within a runtime\" 恐慌错误。"

#: src/advanced/ws-control.md:426
msgid ""
"**u128 workaround in tests**: Daemon test helpers construct WsRequest JSON "
"strings manually via `format!()` + `serde_json::to_string()` (not "
"`serde_json::to_value()`) to preserve `uhlc::ID` u128 values on the wire."
msgstr ""
"**测试中的 u128 变通方案**：守护进程测试辅助函数通过 `format!()` + "
"`serde_json::to_string()`（而非 `serde_json::to_value()`）手动构造 WsRequest "
"JSON 字符串，以保留线上传输的 `uhlc::ID` u128 值。"

#: src/advanced/ws-control.md:428
msgid ""
"**Test coordinator setup**: Both integration and E2E tests use "
"`adora_coordinator::start_testing()` which binds to port 0 (OS-assigned) and "
"accepts an empty external event stream."
msgstr ""
"**测试协调器设置**：集成测试和端到端测试均使用 "
"`adora_coordinator::start_testing()`，该函数绑定到端口 0（由操作系统分配）并"
"接受空的外部事件流。"

