msgid ""
"The key insight: CLI and future web UIs connect to the coordinator via "
"WebSocket. By having the coordinator subscribe to Zenoh on their behalf and "
"forward messages as binary frames, topic inspection works anywhere the "
"WebSocket connection reaches."
